{"tid":2392440,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"GME「軋空大戰」 傳美高梅、Netflix有意改編成電影","createTime":"2021-02-02T20:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T23:21:23.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a475778a1779dfdda3a6878b6bd4d1fb636c0800","tid":2392440,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T20:35:45.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美國reddit鄉民與對沖基金就GameStop的「軋空大戰」引起全球關注，由於此事件太有戲劇張力，美國娛樂新聞網《Deadline Hollywood》在1日的報導中引述消息人士的說法稱，米高梅（MGM）、網飛（Netflix）均有興趣將此事件改編成電影，Netflix甚至還找上奧斯卡最佳原創劇本得主馬克．鮑爾（Mark Boal）。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士向《Deadline》透露，Netflix正在討論將此事件改編成電影，而且找上編劇的是曾以〈危機倒數〉（The Hurt Locker）奪得奧斯卡獎的馬克．鮑爾，並有意找上曾出演〈致所有我曾愛過的男孩〉（To All the Boys I've Loved Before）的諾亞．森迪尼奧（Noah Centineo）作為主角。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3430230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3430230&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrcdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=1bbc8f75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3430230&h=67abeb56\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3430230</a>"},{"pid":"f44100d15675fe8781ece3600040c60b87fbfa8b","tid":2392440,"uid":7736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T20:53:07.000Z","msg":"有冇連燈仔嘅角色？ 我ok ar"},{"pid":"d0cde23fc8e5ef15bb0fab84f446f5c6456fc291","tid":2392440,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T20:54:51.000Z","msg":"都仲未有結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc222b1d19f091789aea127bc589caeb4c8f2a6b","tid":2392440,"uid":176447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T20:55:53.000Z","msg":"拍戲對沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c90f9edc24bcac6c637311b5df49149cd9a21535","tid":2392440,"uid":38267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2